{"tid":176753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抱孫有假放 香港寬頻推3天「添孫假」","createTime":"2017-03-28T11:24:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T11:46:08.000Z","uid":53000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fa1ace7565c7821c3ed6e4e8d699b69b59a82e58","tid":176753,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T11:24:50.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】香港寬頻宣布由本年四月一日起，為剛成為祖父母的員工提供「添孫假」3天，以讓員工全情投入迎接家庭新成員。<br />\n<br />\n香港寬頻表示，添孫假開放予所有本港辦公室人員申請，申請時只需交出一張包括初生嬰兒的三代同堂合照作證明即可。該集團助理總監陳振宇表示，香港寬頻推行「生活工作優次」，相信賦予員工更大自由度去追尋有意義的個人及家庭生活，可令員工幹勁大增，有助提高工作效率和生產力。"},{"pid":"4817d5e777d99e3a6e36c62ac5d6e216fdd369c8","tid":176753,"uid":57462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T11:25:48.000Z","msg":"有幾多人拎到？"},{"pid":"855685257793d127acbb2e7ea8dbbda147494cf3","tid":176753,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T11:36:41.000Z","msg":"只限人材員工，其他冇！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/27/173125_2e5d1a08090fd00bf5c75c1dbfe64ace.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F27%2F173125_2e5d1a08090fd00bf5c75c1dbfe64ace.jpg&h=e5911090&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba9cec8b2dbd54d6bc0c7536145cae32a9973110","tid":176753,"uid":73613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T11:39:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ff5fd730886f3a938d7e71e0ff400bdc457ecbdd","tid":176753,"uid":73613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T11:39:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d312645595dfb91ae9e7553ca32879b07e0a2cb6","tid":176753,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T11:39:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/O46HGDEqM5s/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FO46HGDEqM5s%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=78d5b115&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae13b6051b5918bf8655369c6e9a511f2d403a90","tid":176753,